    dc:description "Figure 6. A–D, Belemnobatis sp., anterior tooth. A, labial view. B, lateral view. C, lingual view. D, occlusal view. E–L, Spathobatis sp. E–H, antero–lateral tooth. E, labial view. F, lateral view. G, lingual view. H, occlusal view. I–L, lateral tooth. I, labial view. J, lateral view. K, lingual view. L, occlusal view. M–P, Rhinobatoidei indet. M, labial view. N, lateral view. O, lingual view. P, occlusal view. Q–T, Rhinobatos sp. Q, labial view. R, lateral view. S, lingual view. T, occlusal view. All scale bars equal 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5445970/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5445972>
    dc:description "Figure 7. A–D, Rhinobatoidei indet. A, labial view. B, lateral view. C, lingual view. D, occlusal. E–T, Platypterix venustulus gen. et. sp. nov. E–H, anterior male tooth. E, labial view. F, lateral view. G, lingual view. H, occlusal view. I–L, lateral male tooth. I, labial view. J, lateral view. K, lingual view. L, occlusal view. M–P, anterior female tooth. M, labial view. N, lateral view. O, lingual view. P, occlusal view. Q–T, lateral female tooth. Q, labial view. R, lateral view. S, lingual view. T, occlusal view. U–X, Celtipristis herreroi (Kriwet, 1999b). U, labial view. V, lateral view. W, lingual view. X, occlusal view. All scale bars equal 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5445972/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

